    <item>
      <title>Re: Troubleshooting view_parameters</title>
      <link>http://projects.ez.no/nvnewsletter/forum/general/troubleshooting_view_parameters/re_troubleshooting_view_parameters</link>
      <description>Hi,&#13;
&#13;
thanks for the feedback.&#13;
&#13;
We haven't made much testing with eZ Flow so I can't provide solution to view parameter issue at the moment. My suggestion is that you try to implement eZ Flow special block which contains subscription form template. Then you should be able to get {$#view_parameters.status} successfully.&#13;
&#13;
There is new version just uploaded which fixes that subscribe redirect. Check doc/changelogs before upgrading.</description>
