      <title>Re: Install problem</title>
      <link>http://projects.ez.no/nvnewsletter/forum/general/install_problem/re_install_problem</link>
      <description>Hi,&#13;
it means that you must create the sender and receiver group via the newsletter - tab in the admin interface. It doesn't mean actual ez user groups. The sender information stores the information which will be shown as the sender of the newsletter. This way you can have different senders for different newsletters. And the receiver group is basically a user group into which you add the newsletter receivers. So in the newsletter - tab, click "receiver groups" at the left side and then "New group" button in the main area. All that is required is a name for that group. After that you can add newsletter receivers to that group. And when you create/send your newsletter you can specify which group you want to send the newsletter to and also which sender information you want to use for it. Did this clear things up?</description>
      <author>community@ez.no (Tuomo Syvänperä)</author>
      <guid>http://projects.ez.no/nvnewsletter/forum/general/install_problem/re_install_problem</guid>
